{"tid":1074924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩賊失手墮坡受傷被捕","createTime":"2019-03-23T17:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T17:36:53.000Z","uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e721dff14c23066b45a12d1b9d082602747581","tid":1074924,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T17:36:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190321/s00001/1553184772751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190321%2Fs00001%2F1553184772751&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=bc610f6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190321%2Fs00001%2F1553184772751&h=d50dbb68\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190321/s00001/1553184772751</a>"},{"pid":"985d5634512c43090dfcb5f80e7a2f159ae51332","tid":1074924,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"荔景鍾山臺曉峰居1期一單位，晚上8時許，女戶主發現窗戶被撬，有被搜掠痕迹，遂報警。警方到場調查時發現一名男子受傷被困對開山坡，經調查後相信他與另一同黨潛入單位爆竊，不排除逃走期間跌傷被困山坡，傷者事後由接報到場消防救起，再由救護車送院治理，他涉嫌爆竊被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步調查，相信有兩名賊人潛入單位爆竊，掠去約4萬元現金、一部相機及4支鏡頭。警員仍在附近山邊搜尋失物及另一名在逃賊人。"}]}